message: #8933 I have a huge crush on you but I can't do anything about it because your roommate has a huge crush on me and you know it, and because of that you can't be with me knowing that I don't like her. Like I know there's protocol for this kind of thing, but I know that if it wasn't for your roommate then I would have a great chance of getting closer to you and that you would let it happen. I feel so unlucky that if you had roomed with anyone else that you and I could be together without hassle

#8924 My exboyfriend who dumped me two months ago for being "bad at long distance" told me he cheated on me while we were still together on Wednesday. Is it bad if I make myself feel better by telling myself I'm way out of his league anyway? He's a piece of shit but it still hurts.
#8919 I kind of feel like a ghost. No one has any idea where or who I am and I just float around in the background. I literally know the professors better than any of my classmates.
